This project is to learn and practice Spring boot.
It is using gradle to build the project.


For sprint boot, followed these videos:
https://javabrains.io/topics/spring/  ---- Spring boot quick start.

For hibernate stuff, followed these videos:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VpUp0QNJ-5M

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OhgJmZEva7A


For session factory, transaction manager, followed this wiki:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/30870146/transactional-annotation-not-working-in-spring-boot

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12337504/hibernatetransactionmanager-or-jpatransactionmanager/12337572
